# qodana-php — Qodana Ultimate for PHP/PhpStorm (image name = repoName). Feed code QDPHP, PUBLIC feed:
# this `.env` OMITS QD_DISTRIBUTION_FEED and relies on lib/dist.dockerfile's public-feed default. Builds
# on the DHI php language base (PHP PRE-BAKED, but NO node and NO composer), so — like qodana-go — it
# LAYERS the node toolchain (NODE_MAJOR) + the in-place eslint pin for JS/TS support, PLUS the composer
# toolchain. Composer is a cross-image COPY (source php.Dockerfile copies it from the upstream composer
# image), so it opens its own php-toolchain stage (FROM base, inheriting node+eslint) and COPYs composer
# from the digest-pinned COMPOSER_IMAGE; DIST_BASE_STAGE=php-toolchain layers the dist onto it (the
# conda/android pattern). The php base does NOT occupy uid 1000 (empirically: /etc/passwd has only
# root/nonroot/_apt/nobody, like the golang base), so qodana-php keeps base.dockerfile's DEFAULT uid 1000
# and sets NO uid keys/build args. eslint is pinned in lib/toolchain/eslint/package.json (renovate-
# tracked), NOT here. Pins are the concrete values in docs/phase-0-decisions.md; EnvContractTest asserts
# byte-identity for QD_VERSION/QD_BUILD/QD_PRODUCT_INFO_CODE, the php base digest, and COMPOSER_IMAGE.
QD_LINTER_SLUG=qodana-php
QD_VERSION=2026.1
QD_BUILD=261.25880
QD_RELEASE_TYPE=release
QD_PRODUCT_INFO_CODE=PS
QD_BASE_IMAGE=dhi.io/php:8.4-dev@sha256:6640324da549fe224c038df12edc886588ea9607cf8121d1424014af1d70d1c6
DIST_BASE_STAGE=php-toolchain
COMPOSER_IMAGE=composer:2.10.0@sha256:1b73755de4f19775ba6087fd5313664493e06fab72b6fc27dc2044e87bb7c4c3
CLI_BINARY=qodana
CLI_VERSION=2026.2
CLI_OS=linux
NODE_MAJOR=20
